      "markText": "胡适没有回答，而是问提问题的是哪一个。当他得知毛泽东是没有注册的学生时，这位激进而洒脱的教授给了毛泽东一个难堪，他拒绝回答问题。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2426&rangeEnd=2490",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2426&rangeEnd=2490"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_8_3157-3210",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3157-3210",
      "markText": "就在毛泽东整天想着如何走出韶山冲时，罗氏患了重病回到娘家，很快就在两年孤独且无望的婚姻中熬到了自己的卒时。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3157&rangeEnd=3210",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3157&rangeEnd=3210"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_4_4130-4196",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4130-4196",
      "markText": "他那永远都在忙碌的母亲就像一座永远不会倒下的灯塔，无论是惊涛骇浪还是风吹雨打，她都会屹立着，发着光，让他的眼前永远充满着光明与温暖。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4130&rangeEnd=4196",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4130&rangeEnd=4196"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_34_2453-2485",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "2453-2485",
      "markText": "在当时，中央苏区几乎所有的红军领导和红军干部都要丢下自己的孩子。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=2453&rangeEnd=2485",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=2453&rangeEnd=2485"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_29_2381-2409",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "2381-2409",
      "markText": "年仅29岁的杨开慧在长沙城浏阳门外的识字岭被国民党枪决。",
      "totalCount": 50,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=2381&rangeEnd=2409",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=2381&rangeEnd=2409"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_12_4426-4500",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "4426-4500",
      "markText": "毛泽东后来还多次提倡既读有字之书，又读“无字之书”，向社会学习，向实际学习，向群众学习，反对死读书，读死书。注重读“无字之书”，注重实践，注重对中国",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=4426&rangeEnd=4500",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=4426&rangeEnd=4500"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_35_2402-2483",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "2402-2483",
      "markText": "中共中央政治局在这里召开了一次政治局扩大会议，讨论中央红军如何走出生死存亡的困境。参加会议的除政治局委员和候补委员外，还有红军总部和各军团负责人，以及邓小平等人。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=2402&rangeEnd=2483",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=2402&rangeEnd=2483"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_23_6692-6763",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "6692-6763",
      "markText": "有生就有死，有起点就有终点。49年后的这一天。一生都在奔跑的毛泽东跑到了生命终点。这位旷古奇人永不服输的心脏跳动声，结束在9月9日零点10分。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=6692&rangeEnd=6763",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=6692&rangeEnd=6763"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_35_4014-4055",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "4014-4055",
      "markText": "他觉得自己的这位战友、这位同志，是真正的共产主义者，在他身上有一种水晶一般的品质。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=4014&rangeEnd=4055",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=4014&rangeEnd=4055"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_40_3753-3823",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "3753-3823",
      "markText": "贺子珍最后也和全国人民一样，是在毛泽东纪念堂里与毛泽东相见的。这就是为毛泽东先后生育过六个子女，一同度过最为艰难困苦的岁月的一个女人的命运。",
      "totalCount": 44,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=3753&rangeEnd=3823",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=3753&rangeEnd=3823"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_4_1475-1552",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1475-1552",
      "markText": "咳！我们知道了！我们醒觉了！天下者我们的天下。国家者我们的国家。社会者我们的社会。我们不说，谁说？我们不干，谁干？刻不容缓的民众大联合，我们应该积极进行。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1475&rangeEnd=1552",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1475&rangeEnd=1552"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_14_583-634",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "583-634",
      "markText": "毛泽东返回长沙后，到长沙修业小学任教，所以在毛泽东的履历中有一段做教师的经历，便是指的这段时间的职业。",
      "totalCount": 40,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=583&rangeEnd=634",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=583&rangeEnd=634"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_7_1160-1223",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1160-1223",
      "markText": "他最早接触的小说是《盛世危言》，这些书在父亲的眼里就是闲书、杂书、无用的书，不能管吃不能管喝，在这一点上父亲对儿子是不满意的。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1160&rangeEnd=1223",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1160&rangeEnd=1223"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_6_4673-4722",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4673-4722",
      "markText": "比如，接济别人，同情善良，与人平等，而自己则节衣缩食，生活简朴，身为一国之首，却过着普通人的生活。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4673&rangeEnd=4722",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4673&rangeEnd=4722"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_7_2498-2545",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2498-2545",
      "markText": "父亲是在气头上说的话，可躲进竹林里的毛泽东真的不敢回家了，火暴性子的父亲不把他往死里打才怪呢！",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2498&rangeEnd=2545",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2498&rangeEnd=2545"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_10_2106-2175",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2106-2175",
      "markText": "毛泽东从表兄手里拿到这两份书报如获至宝，字斟句酌地读着。书报中倡导的民主进取精神和变法维新运动，使求知若渴的毛泽东备感兴趣，精神为之一振。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=640972&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2106&rangeEnd=2175",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0a3322c059c7cc0a3651d39?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2106&rangeEnd=2175"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "640972_13_2007-2100",
